tool_description:
You provide coordinates(latitude, longitude) and api returns height map.
Heightmap is black & white png image where the brightest pixel has the most elevation.
name: Heightmap from Latitude and Longitude
title: Heightmap from Latitude and Longitude

api_list.name: get heightmap from two geopoints
api_list.description: you provide two geopoints( latitude, longitude). Server returns image/png with heightmap within this borders.
